01T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"好地地唔得既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:33:09.000Z","msg":"当初他们禁止食用猫肉；<br />\n我没有说话，我不吃猫肉。<br />\n<br />\n接着他们禁止食用狗肉；<br />\n我没有说话，我不吃狗肉。<br />\n<br />\n然后他们禁止食用兔肉；<br />\n我没有说话，我不吃兔肉。<br />\n<br />\n后来他们禁止食用驴肉；<br />\n我没有说话，我不吃驴肉。<br />\n<br />\n现在他们禁止食用猪肉；<br />\n到这时，已经没有人可以替我说话了。"},{"pid":"f772dcd65c906c903a8030b4e966b8a9097f1b06","tid":576372,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:34:03.000Z","msg":"不能完全打死！廣東驚見水煮活貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20120309/30559.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20120309%2F30559.htm&d=KAJfYNLaML4WSuj7codgJE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=99df0d8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20120309/30559.htm</a>"},{"pid":"765461f6b30d819000ba9c2634af6e2cb3185e44","tid":576372,"uid":192,"like":10,"dislike":27,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:36:09.000Z","msg":"餐廳賣貓肉已經10年，這些餐廳大都讓客人到貓籠挑選，當廚師進貓籠捉貓，就會聽到一陣陣悽慘的貓叫聲。廚師說招牌菜叫「水煮活貓」，他們先用鐵鉗夾住貓的脖子，右手拿鐵棍狠砸貓頭，然後再把貓甩到地上，繼續用鐵棍猛砸貓的腦袋，他強調「不能完全打死，還要用水煮一下，這叫活煮貓」。當貓漸漸昏厥時，廚師再將幾乎斷氣的貓扔進滾燙熱水裡。<br />\n淒厲的慘叫聲從滾燙的熱水鍋傳來，廚師再拿一根粗木棍，不斷地打貓頭和身體補充說：「這樣打出來的貓肉口感才好。」把貓煮熟後，再脫毛切片，這道菜才完成。<br />\n雖然過程慘忍無道，仍供不應求，主因是食客認為吃貓肉可治哮喘和類風濕，才絡繹不絕。隔壁撞球店老闆表示，夏天來吃貓肉的較少，一到冬天，門前的車要排到街尾，全是熟客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 流晒口水"},{"pid":"d6a17496d6183d2fe4f7547cfbcb6eb85d8eda17","tid":576372,"uid":49955,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:42:03.000Z","msg":"食狗肉咪算囉<br />\n貓係人類既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e43abe40b6f997431a96f988922fe63cbbd2160","tid":576372,"uid":192,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:42:14.000Z","msg":"Lion eats cat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/thYHQFZL82U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FthYHQFZL82U&d=KAJfYNLaML4WSuj7codgJE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=63843009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/thYHQFZL82U</a>"},{"pid":"4c3fc5da90eb5fa211fbb77b310714341e0200ba","tid":576372,"uid":192,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d6a17496d6183d2fe4f7547cfbcb6eb85d8eda17","tid":576372,"uid":49955,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:42:03.000Z","msg":"食狗肉咪算囉<br />\n貓係人類既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:43:04.000Z","msg":"對我黎講牛先係人類朋友"},{"pid":"5f73ebaed3ed5f67de1dd3b770ef2162ad90a5b4","tid":576372,"uid":16061,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:43:58.000Z","msg":"attention seeker<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec54c6f759d647828ad7a04d928c1d244de9fa0","tid":576372,"uid":192,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f73ebaed3ed5f67de1dd3b770ef2162ad90a5b4","tid":576372,"uid":16061,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:43:58.000Z","msg":"attention seeker<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:45:00.000Z","msg":"咩食貓肉真係咁難令你地接受咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43724bbd6c168ac00b4b633de8c851e8ac6d6381","tid":576372,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"q